+  "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds an experimental hidden `--use-agent-commander` solve option. By default, hive-mind continues to use the existing embedded adapters for `claude`, `codex`, `opencode`, and `agent`. When the flag is explicitly set, solve and restart iterations route tool execution through `agent-commander`.\n\n## What Changed\n\n- Added `src/agent-commander.lib.mjs` as the opt-in adapter around `agent-commander@0.4.3`.\n- Added hidden `--use-agent-commander` to `SOLVE_OPTION_DEFINITIONS`; `hive` forwards it through the existing solve passthrough option map.\n- Wired the flag into initial solve execution, tool connection validation, uncommitted-change handling, and watch/auto-restart tool iterations.\n- Preserved the default embedded execution path when the flag is absent.\n- Updated `agent-commander` from `^0.4.2` to `^0.4.3` for prompt-file support needed by large hive-mind prompts.\n- Added a default-suite regression test covering option defaults, hive passthrough, controller option mapping, validation dry-run behavior, execution/result normalization, and cost/session summary extraction.\n- Added `docs/case-studies/issue-1043/` with collected issue/PR/package evidence, requirements, compatibility notes, and upstream gap tracking.\n\n## Upstream Follow-Up\n\nOpened focused issues for missing full-parity surfaces in `agent-commander`:\n\n- https://github.com/link-assistant/agent-commander/issues/29\n- https://github.com/link-assistant/agent-commander/issues/30\n\n## Verification\n\n- `npx eslint src/agent-commander.lib.mjs src/solve.mjs src/solve.restart-shared.lib.mjs src/solve.validation.lib.mjs src/solve.config.lib.mjs tests/test-agent-commander-option.mjs`\n- `npm run lint`\n- `node tests/test-agent-commander-option.mjs`\n- `node tests/test-hive-solve-option-parity.mjs`\n- `node tests/test-issue-1718-hive-passthrough-false.mjs`\n- `npm test` (all 80 selected test files passed)\n- `bash scripts/check-file-line-limits.sh` (passed; existing near-limit warnings only)\n\n\n\nFixes #1043",
